        We will constitute 5 groups of patients very well phenotyped and with liver biopsy (with at
        our disposal frozen liver tissue, paraffin-embedded liver tissue and serum for all the
        patients):

          1. steatosis group (n=10);

          2. NASH group without fibrosis (n=10);

          3. moderate fibrosis (n=10);

          4. advanced fibrosis (n=10);

          5. Control group (n=10).
